    pages = "845--860",
    year = "2017",
    textVersion = "Daru, B. H., Elliott, T. L., Park, D. S. & Davies, T. J. (2017), Understanding the Processes Underpinning Patterns of Phylogenetic Regionalization. Trends in Ecology and Evolution, 32: 845--860. doi: 10.1016/j.tree.2017.08.013"
)
